com.adobe.livecycle.content.repository.action

Interface TypeExtensionActionHandler

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ActionHandler

    public interface TypeExtensionActionHandler
extends ActionHandler
    The extension handler interface will enable template type extension during deployment. This class will not get any AssetObject in it. It will get the template type and class as parameter and will return a list of extension properties in the map. It is expected that preprocessor implementation of this interface will provide all the extended properties in the passed map with key as TypeExtensionActionHandler.TYPE_EXTENSION_KEY. If there are multiple handlers that are adding properties then they should keep on adding their properties to the List if it is already there in the map.
